      {
        "view": "redmine-explorer-timer",
        "contents": "No plan for today.\n[Plan Your Day](command:redmine.timer.planDay)\n\n---\n\n**Tips:**\n- Right-click units for more actions\n- `Ctrl+Y T` toggles timer\n- Click a unit to start/pause",
